                <p class="mb-4">
                    Catalytic Converter: Reduces harmful emissions by converting pollutants into less harmful gases.
                </p>
                <p class="mb-4">
                    Silencer (Muffler): Reduces the noise produced by the engine's exhaust gases.
                <p class="mb-4">
